# 📊 Learning Tracker

A beginner-friendly data analysis project built using Python, Pandas, Seaborn, and Matplotlib to visualize learning progress, practice hours, projects completed, and confidence levels.

## 🚀 Features
- Data visualization
- Learning progress analysis
- Correlation heatmap
- Beginner-friendly EDA

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- Seaborn
- Matplotlib